{"tid":1317643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員手指一節被咬斷，真相係，咬人者乃正當自衛","createTime":"2019-07-14T20:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:51:31.000Z","uid":264806,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2593025ef44201b919100850b8d17e8668dafbe4","tid":1317643,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:04:30.000Z","msg":"有無呢兩張圖片既原新聞片段？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXsvpu4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXsvpu4.png&h=01f3242c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dne9E3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDne9E3q.png&h=6820ddbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有既話，佢就可以系庭上說明，當時佢係出於正當既自衛行為-------因為有警員正在插佢眼，於是該警員隻手至放左系佢面上。佢唔咬落去制止該警員既話，佢隨時會盲！<br />\n<br />\n(我估佢會被控襲警及嚴重傷害他人身體。所以要有呢點「正當自衛」黎抗辯！)"},{"pid":"a3f31732b55af11aaa6afc658ef19e0311e807c4","tid":1317643,"uid":21861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:06:23.000Z","msg":"係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自然反應</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ab263bb0a3b194913be36c3f270789abe7423c6c","tid":1317643,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:07:09.000Z","msg":"痛成咁係人都咬緊牙關啦 本能反應姐冇心"},{"pid":"a32eb0fa56e1b66d0bce26c939d13975c601f746","tid":1317643,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a3f31732b55af11aaa6afc658ef19e0311e807c4","tid":1317643,"uid":21861,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:06:23.000Z","msg":"係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自然反應</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:08:43.000Z","msg":"拿 首先呢就係隻警犬用手指插人個口先嘅<br />\n另一隻手插人地隻眼 <br />\n自然反應下灰衫個人就合埋個口<br />\n咁條警犬隻手指咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一句講曬啦 自作孽不可活"},{"pid":"1cd113165482dd320474d9c9367acf379ba84242","tid":1317643,"uid":26480